# Large binary tarballs of the raw PDB set (~1.1 GB combined).
# Tracked via Git LFS to keep the plain-Git working tree lean and to avoid
# the >2 GB repo-size warning from GitHub/GitLab.
#
# To fetch the tarballs after cloning:
#   git lfs install        # once per machine
#   git lfs pull           # inside this repo
#
# If you do not have git-lfs installed, the tarballs will appear as small
# plaintext pointer files. Install git-lfs
# (https://git-lfs.com) or download the tarballs out-of-band.
data/structures/*.tar.gz filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
